Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------SUB-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  乃木坂同学很了解男性的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪里有  一般般而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用谦虚  我曾经得到过你的好建议
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在班里也大受好评哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是无所不知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一位男性邀请去约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约…约会？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是从很早前就彼此熟识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却是第一次邀请我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂同学  请问约会时到底要做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了今后的打算请你赐教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我吧  乃木坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就特别指导你们一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在恬静的咖啡店中边品尝红茶边谈笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是个不错的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对面坐着  彼此注视的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连时间的流逝都能忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼  彼此注视…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后就可以两人一起去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  要温柔地牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵  牵着手？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以  太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  两人是恋人的话就无须介意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去电影院之类的也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影院
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在安静的地方  两人互相依偎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的气氛将会与电影一起达到最高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在这种季节里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能在约会的最后两人去祭典和烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在游玩了店摊后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观赏在夜空中绽放的美丽烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人在此接下第一吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受益匪浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然顺势就说了那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也没约会过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  因为美夏小姐能看得上眼的男性少得可怜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说根本就没机会相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校又是只有大小姐的女子学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上学放学都是专车接送
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说我身边的男性  也就爸爸和大哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我也像姐姐那样选普通的学校就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐自从夏漫展事件后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情比以前更积极了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那父母公认的情侣今天也是约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  裕人先生来访
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在春香小姐的房里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  现在是单独相处中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我还是无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  不是说好了要相信春香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干涉他们的事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让年轻的男女单独相处太不纯洁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的意思是说我们的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做需要瞒着父母的不纯洁的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我也不是这种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们无关呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为妹妹担心姐姐也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是作为乃木坂家的女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变…变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我看清楚一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的  大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的也是  这么热…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们再亲热也还不能做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏？  那波？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥你们才是在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在做煎饼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正马上就到喝茶的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为焦了一点  所以有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦  我不也做得大过头了  而且翻面的时候还失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎饼…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又干这些让人误解的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要深究了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做奇怪的猜想了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经烤好了  要不要一起来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想您肯定会这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以准备好了足够大家的份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是叶月  大家一起来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸直到昨天为止都还在一个叫五角大楼的地方出差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月似乎还去了一个叫摩萨德的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后小秋就弄翻了咖喱乌冬面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就在那时大量葱头袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的海藻和麦麸怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  作业完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还差很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那波  你认为今天姐姐他们如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为非常亲密  非常友好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真  那波你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像将炼乳一口气喝下一般的天真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}注：日语甜和天真发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐跨越了特殊爱好的墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不久前还发生了那种事件  也过关了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是两人的感情还是没什么进展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边吃着煎饼蛋糕边聊天  气氛完全起不来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是非常令人担忧的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就那个性格  不主动一些也没什么可说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是问题在于大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐那么可爱  而且条件也都齐全了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然悠哉地聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这必须想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要告诉大哥哥  恋人是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是按计划行事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人就会更加亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后将留下甜蜜的夏日回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏小姐太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  马上展开行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  我是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美夏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听出来了啊  不愧是恋人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有些事想谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周的星期天有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空是有空  不过是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吧  乱七八糟的很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之绝对要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那星期天10点在车站见  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…刚才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那个…那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  竟然让女孩子等你  完全不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是姐姐的话该如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你这打扮算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是你平常穿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是约会  就应该穿好一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  今天是我和大哥哥的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我进行约会的指导？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  在旁边看得我着急死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐又像那样非常迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想只有让大哥哥积极起来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这话算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我为了你们而帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归根到底  大哥哥你就满足现状了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得出来玩一次  却光是在聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又形不成好气氛  一天就结束了说拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这样的关系也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你想等姐姐行动的话就会一直这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的话该出手时就出手  该干就干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我才来传授你恋爱的奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的奥义啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说进了这种气氛好的咖啡店的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用聊动画和作业的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是互相注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要崩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像刚才那样保护好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是迟钝的姐姐也会心跳不止的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就该牵起手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  跟姐姐的时候要大哥哥主动去牵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刚…刚才还挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快点继续吧  接下来是看电影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放弃您的这份思念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  辉夜姬  如果是为了您的话  就算是蓬莱之地…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电影院里该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人靠在一起  总之要依偎着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在看电影  也告诉姐姐你的心是向着她的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教人的人怎么先睡着了  这该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊～  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌～大哥哥好色哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什  什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏  好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏  我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是为了让你引以为戒而作的失败的范例
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  接下来我们去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  我们去参加河边的烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我把姐姐也叫上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是日本舞的练习结束以后  就会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会见机行事  让你们俩独处的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好把握机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我尽力而为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要牵着手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对  做得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然周日人很多啊  小心不要走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这是在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这不是裕人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这不是乃木坂同学的妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  什么  今天和妹妹两人约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有了我你还这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要说这种让人误会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎菜  接下来要去庙会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去看每年一度的河边烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身浴衣  真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我最中意的一款
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜难得穿一回浴衣  但看的人却全是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二学期开始以后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生们还会记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  如果忘记了的话  到时候我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  烟花大会  裕人你们也一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了  真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂…到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定变更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明明有我在旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人还谈的那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说  我和他们不同校  也不同年级
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天是我和大哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  但是为什么我会生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这身衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～挺合身的  看上去感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么感想要发表吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣很适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还要别人提醒  扣分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是姐姐的话  记得要立刻夸奖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去参加烟花大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢  真壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的话  看不见烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气  难得的烟花看不见就太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一清二楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后这里很完美哦  这样的话一定能和姐姐进展顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大哥哥要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:18:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然麻烦你教了我很多  我却不得要领给你添了很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事  没有这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是我想出来的怪念头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我今天也很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是头一次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然发生了不少事  但是大哥哥很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  和美夏一起度过的一天很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太温柔了  被你这样说的话我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花大会还没结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  接下来才是高潮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  春香这套浴衣很适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最中意的一套
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多该放我下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也过来了  也不能就一直这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  下来的话就看不见烟花了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我并不介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这个问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天玩得可真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那波…莫非你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样开心的美夏小姐  我还是头一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快看烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 早上好酸乳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家暑假过得愉快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了  明明是对方邀请的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正…反正像我这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师  抱怨就到这  差不多该班会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  就算再怎么消沉也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然分手了  找下一位就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里  我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到今年文化祭的时节了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:21:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  各个班级都要选出男女各一名作为文化祭执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁想当候选人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  作为班里的节目负责人和联络人很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我要当执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要当执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚转学过来  想要快些融入班级里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是积极参加这种学校活动比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起  天宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么男生的话  裕君就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么要我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为两人看上去关系蛮不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且座位也紧挨着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就帮帮天宫同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为报答  老师我给你做舒服的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  如果是裕人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:22:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  裕人  裕人  裕人  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  裕人  裕人  裕人  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  如果我可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么两位  上台来和大家打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次作为文化祭执行委员的  天宫椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名写作  天气的天  宫成县的宫  椎树的椎  菜叶的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座右铭是  先发制人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙历前793年  帝国历前1103年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑裕人成为了文化祭的执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这只不过是新争斗的开幕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.89,0:24:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  乃木坂春香的秘密  第九话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.97,0:24:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.35,0:24:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河的历史  又翻开了新的一页


